---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';

const lastUpdated = 'March 2025';
const siteUrl = 'https://www.generatorgators.com';
const companyEmail = 'info@generatorgators.com';
---

<Layout
  title="Privacy Policy | Generator Gators"
  description="Generator Gators privacy policy. Learn how we collect, use, and protect your personal information when you use our generator installation matching service."
>

  <!-- HERO -->
  <section class="bg-green-900 text-white py-12 px-4">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-extrabold mb-3">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="text-green-200">Last Updated: {lastUpdated}</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CONTENT -->
  <section class="py-14 px-4 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto prose prose-gray max-w-none">

      <div class="bg-yellow-50 border border-yellow-200 rounded-xl p-5 mb-8 text-sm text-gray-700">
        <strong>Summary:</strong> Generator Gators is a free matching service. We collect contact information you submit through our quote forms to connect you with local generator installation partners. We do not sell your personal information to third parties beyond our vetted installer network.
      </div>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">1. Who We Are</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
        Generator Gators ("we," "us," or "our") operates the website {siteUrl}. We are a referral and matching service that connects homeowners with vetted local standby generator installation professionals. We do not install generators ourselves.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">2. Information We Collect</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 mb-3">We collect information you provide directly when you submit a quote request through our website, including:</p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-600 space-y-1 mb-4">
        <li>Full name</li>
        <li>Phone number</li>
        <li>Zip code / address information</li>
        <li>Service needs and preferences</li>
      </ul>
      <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
        We may also collect technical information automatically when you visit our website, including IP address, browser type, pages visited, and referring URLs, through standard web analytics tools.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">3. How We Use Your Information</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 mb-3">We use the information we collect to:</p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-600 space-y-1 mb-4">
        <li>Match you with vetted local generator installation partners in your area</li>
        <li>Respond to your inquiries and requests</li>
        <li>Send you information relevant to your generator installation request</li>
        <li>Improve our website and services</li>
        <li>Comply with legal obligations</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">4. How We Share Your Information</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
        When you submit a quote request, your contact information will be shared with one or more vetted generator installation partners in our network who serve your area. These partners may contact you by phone or email to discuss your installation needs and provide a quote.
      </p>
      <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
        We do not sell, rent, or trade your personal information to unrelated third parties, advertising networks, or data brokers.
      </p>
      <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
        We may share information with service providers who assist in operating our website (such as form processing services), subject to confidentiality obligations.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">5. Cookies and Tracking Technologies</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
        Our website may use cookies and similar technologies for analytics and functionality purposes. We may use Google Analytics to understand how visitors use our site. You can opt out of Google Analytics by using the Google Analytics opt-out browser add-on.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">6. Data Retention</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
        We retain your contact information for as long as necessary to fulfill the purposes for which it was collected, including providing our matching service and complying with legal obligations.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">7. Your Rights</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 mb-3">You have the right to:</p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-600 space-y-1 mb-4">
        <li>Request access to the personal information we hold about you</li>
        <li>Request correction of inaccurate information</li>
        <li>Request deletion of your personal information</li>
        <li>Opt out of further communications from us</li>
      </ul>
      <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
        To exercise any of these rights, please contact us at <a href={`mailto:${companyEmail}`} class="text-green-700 underline">{companyEmail}</a>.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">8. Children's Privacy</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
        Our services are not directed to children under the age of 13. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children under 13. If you believe we have collected information from a child, please contact us immediately.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">9. Security</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
        We implement reasonable administrative, technical, and physical safeguards to protect your personal information. However, no method of transmission over the internet or electronic storage is 100% secure, and we cannot guarantee absolute security.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">10. Third-Party Links</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
        Our website may contain links to third-party websites. We are not responsible for the privacy practices of those sites. We encourage you to review the privacy policies of any third-party sites you visit.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">11. Changes to This Policy</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
        We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. We will post any changes on this page and update the "Last Updated" date. Your continued use of our website after changes are posted constitutes your acceptance of the updated policy.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">12. Contact Us</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
        If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy or our data practices, please contact us:
      </p>
      <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-xl p-5 text-gray-700">
        <p class="font-semibold mb-1">Generator Gators</p>
        <p>Email: <a href={`mailto:${companyEmail}`} class="text-green-700 underline">{companyEmail}</a></p>
        <p>Website: <a href={siteUrl} class="text-green-700 underline">{siteUrl}</a></p>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>
